formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. SERVA SHANTI PROPERTIES PVT LTD(SSPL) HAS TAKEN SECURED LOANS OF 5 CRORES
FROM KMBL. THERE ARE 2 WINGS IN THE PROJECT VIZ. SIDDHI VINAYAK ARCADE BLOCK A AND SIDDHI VINAYAK
ARCADE BLOCK B. BOTH WINGS ARE HAVING DIFFERENT RERA REGISTRATIONS. HOWEVER, LOANS HAVE BEEN
BIFURCATED INTO TWO WINGS EQUALLY AND INTEREST ON LOAN IS APPORTIONED IN THE RATIO OF 60PC AND
40PC FOR BLOCK A AND BLOCK B RESPECTIVELY. SINCE, THE LOAN IS IN THE NAME OF SSPL, TOTAL AMOUNT HAS
BEEN SHOWN IN THE DETAILS ABOVE.
2.AS PER INFORMATION PROVIDED, ALL THE AMOUNTS RECEIVED IN THE RERA BANK ACCOUNT ARE TOWARDS
THE BOOKINGS FOR THE PROJECT. HENCE, THE AMOUNT WITHDRAWN FROM THE RERA BANK ACCOUNT IS
CONSIDERED AS WITHDRAWAL FOR THE PROJECT.
3.THE PROMOTER HAS NOT MAINTAINED PROPER ACCOUNTING RECORDS OF COSTS INCURRED AND PAID
BECAUSE OF THE COMPLEXITIES IN MAINTAINING BOOKS OF ACCOUNTS, AS MORE THAN 2 PROJECTS ARE
UNDERTAKEN IN THE SAME COMPANY. HENCE, WE HAVE CONSIDERED COST INCURRED AS PAID FOR THE
PURPOSE OF FORM 3.
4.THE IDENTIFICATION OF CARPET AREA IS NOT POSSIBLE. THE CARPET AREA CANNOT BE CHANGED IN FORM 3A
FURTHER. HENCE, WE HAVE TAKEN THE CARPET AREA AS IT WAS APPLIED AT THE TIME OF RERA REGISTRATION.
5.THE DETAILS OF UNSECURED LOANS, IF ANY, HAVE NOT BEEN PROVIDED. HENCE, DETAILS OF USL ARE NOT
SHOWN.
6. THE DETAILS OF OUTSTANDING SECURED LOANS ARE TAKEN AS PER THE RELEVANT WORKINGS AND RECORDS PROVIDED.
7. THE AMOUNT WITHDRAWN FROM RERA BANK A/C IS MORE THAN COST INCURRED AS PER BOOKS OF ACCOUNTS. THE PROJECT HAS RECEIVED BU PERMISSION BUT 10 MEMBERS ARE NOT THERE, THE CRITERIA OF FORMATION OF SOCIETY IS NOT FULFILLED AND SOCIETY CANNOT BE FORMED. THE COMPLETION UNDER RERA IS HENCEFORTH NOT APPLIED WITH. THEREFORE, AMOUNTS IN EXCESS OF COST INCURRED ARE WITHDRAWN FROM RERA A/C AS BU PERMISSION IS RECEIVED AND PROJECT  IS COMPLETED
